This box set was much more interesting than the previous 2 box stets, Naruto finally faces the Nine-Tailed Fox & takes control of it's Chakra. It also tells the story of what really happened exactly 16 years ago, when the 9 tails first attacked & it tells more about what happened to Naruto's parents. Everyone prepares for the 4th Great Ninja War to begin, including Tobi going to the Hidden Rain Village & fights Konan. This box set is epic, all of the episodes I think are interesting except for the last episode which was a past event.
